      • Serialized Fields

        • appliedJobAds
          List<JobAd> appliedJobAds
          A list of job ads the candidate has applied for

          This is a many-to-many relationship with JobAd It uses a join table named "applied_jobs" to manage the association.

          Circular references are avoided with @JsonIgnoreProperties annotation.

        • cvFile
          byte[] cvFile
          The candidate's CV file, stored as a byte array. Can be used to store the CV document in binary format.

    • Class com.dreamwork.model.user.Recruiter

      class Recruiter extends User implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • jobAds
          List<JobAd> jobAds
          A list of job ads created by the recruiter.

          This is a one-to-many relationship with JobAd. Cascade operations are enabled to propagate changes from the recruiter to their associated job ads. Circular references are avoided with JsonIgnore annotation.
